ActIndian Act
SubjectSaskatchewan Power Corporation - Easement Peter Ballantyne Cree Nation Band
PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the use by SASKATCHEWAN POWER CORPORATION of its statutory power to take an interest in certain lands within PELICAN NARROWS INDIAN RESERVE N° 184B, PELICAN NARROWS INDIAN RESERVE N° 206, AND SOKATISEWIN SAKAHIKAN INDIAN RESERVE N° 224; and (b) granting Saskatchewan Power Corporation the easement they require, in lieu thereof.
